Titolo: Mahjong Soul

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Mahjong Soul (Chinese: 雀魂麻将; pinyin: Què Hún Májiàng, Japanese: 雀魂 -じゃんたま-, romanized: Jankon -Jantama-) is an browser-based online free-to-play tabletop game about mahjong created by Cat Food Studio and Yostar. It was released in June 2018 in China and in April 2019 in Japan and worldwide, also for Android and iOS devices. An anime television series adaptation by Scooter Films titled Mahjong Soul Pong (じゃんたま PONG☆, Jantama Pong☆) is scheduled to air from April 2022.